Ive learned so much just being here at school. It's amazing how much you learn about yourself. I feel like life here is a huge rollercoaster. Everyday there are ups and downs, sometimes more downs than ups haha but still....haha whatever...rollercoasters... anyway, im really glad i have met the people that I have. Thanks to all the worst people i've ever met..haha..no offense, but you've helped me realize the kind of person that i will never want to be, or ever be around,or associate myself with. AND...thanks to all the wonderful people that i have met that make me realize that life and relationships dont have to be so hard....ever.
    I have learned in some respects to stand up for myself..hahah sometimes...but i am gonna start standing up for myself more and not listening to people that aren't worth my time( I'm sure they are worth other peoples time, but certainly not mine). :)
    Anway, i'ts amazing when I meet great people, how great i feel. haha Why don't i just surround myself with these people all the time? I dont know....It's tough getting away from the people i used to be so close with when i first came to school. But I have to because im dying and withering away over here. I feel like such a bad person all the time. Instead of focusing on the good things that i have, all my attention is taken away by the thoughts of these stupid people. By people, i mean person, and by stupid, i mean ridiculously stupid. :) That's mean, but so very true :)
    Anyway, im just venting, and im not going to proofread, haha im too lazy and i want a nap really bad.
